name: De Candolim Deck Restaurant & Bar

reviews.review_text: We have visited there and has fish fry, chicken tikka pizza, creamy caramel accompanied with 2 drinks. The food is good, but the live music was horrible, don't know who was the singer on Jan 31 , 2025 eve, but he was pathetic , can't engage any of his audiences and his choice of songs were also pathetic! However the ambience is good , it is located near Vaddi of Candolim.
We visited in the afternoon when it was pretty empty. Had watermelon feta salad which was nicely made. Beer rates are reasonable. Washroom was clean and maintained.

It was one of those places that seemed to have everything in place. They had good interiors, christmas decor, in-house bar and live music, good selection of dishes and an open air ambience as well. The goan cuisine and even the curries are definitely worth trying. Prices are reasonable and its open late in the night as well. It's very close to Candolim beach and attracts good tourist crowd.

description:
**De Candolim Deck Restaurant & Bar: A Culinary Haven by the Beach**

Nestled in the vibrant locale of Candolim, De Candolim Deck Restaurant & Bar has garnered an impressive overall rating of 4.2 from over 3,600 enthusiastic patrons. Known for its invigorating ambiance and delightful offerings, the establishment is particularly praised for live music experiences, refreshing beer selection, and a mouthwatering pizza selection, highlighted in the reviews from its visitors.

**Ambiance & Design**

As you approach De Candolim Deck, the inviting ambiance greets you with a blend of captivating interiors. The restaurant features tasteful Christmas décor, an in-house bar that gleams under ambient lighting, and an open-air seating arrangement that encourages guests to savor their meals while basking in the nearby seaside vibes. The layout is both spacious and cozy, making it the perfect spot for a casual afternoon or an evening out with friends. Reviewers noted how the ambiance felt lively, with occasional live music—a feature that adds to the restaurant's charm, yet is met with mixed reviews regarding the quality of performers.

![De Candolim Deck Ambiance](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmSPqKFmk5RZoLVXDlhnb10c5vhd21waJb7p7w8eQiygeGhED1KkOZ6KagZZ-ykOzrEa41zPkvs5t7Vk1YJTRDJrKwRnr7i407k_j1r7KLTy9FwWZJy_M_OGFFv02Dww1OQjeybrQ=w750-h563-p)

**Menu & Culinary Experience**

The offerings at De Candolim Deck are diverse and pleasing to the palate. Signature dishes include the delectable chicken tikka pizza and well-received seafood options like fish fry, which, while might have received some feedback on preparation, still shine as robust choices. The menu caters to various dietary needs, showcasing a balanced array of vegetarian and non-vegetarian options that embody local Goan flavors alongside international dishes. Customers appreciate the presentation, particularly the thoughtfully arranged dishes and fresh ingredients, making every meal an inviting visual feast.

![De Candolim Deck Food Presentation](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdn1SXy5Nom-tq_fbzzM3KXtSyrdzqFVdiAjLJv-XtPST_fDzmWNNtJVJ8qNKcQD6X9MOpWK0tD67zqRdjYonFigNf2cAFd7XhD5mDvGBvHEpXvm6pI8aNTzCIxG9LZKHeqQhgA7=w375-h281-p)

**Customer Experience & Service**

Service at De Candolim Deck is generally well-regarded, with staff being described as friendly and efficient. Customers have found the beer prices quite reasonable, further enhancing their dining experience. The cleanliness of the washroom facilities also earns points for maintaining an overall pleasant atmosphere. While the live music adds to the restaurant's allure, it does appear that on certain occasions, like the review on January 31st, the entertainment may not hit the mark for every guest. Reservations seem to be a wise choice, especially during peak times, as the location does draw a bustling tourist crowd.

**Popularity & Reviews**

With a solid rating and numerous positive testimonials, De Candolim Deck frequently attracts both locals and tourists. The combination of a lively setting, solid food offerings, and an overall welcoming vibe ensures that it holds a significant place in the hearts of its visitors. Social media buzz reflects a positive sentiment, especially around the restaurant's live music events and delicious food, while the Instagram-worthy visuals from patrons continue to promote the venue as a must-visit spot in Candolim.

**Utilizing Visual Content**

The restaurant’s overall vibe is beautifully captured in customer-submitted photos, showcasing both the picturesque surroundings and the culinary delights served on the plates. The bright, lively images reflect not only the joyous dining experiences but also bolster the invitation to potential new guests to come and explore what De Candolim Deck has to offer.

In summary, De Candolim Deck Restaurant & Bar stands out as an ideal culinary destination, combining great food, a lively atmosphere, and memorable experiences—all mere steps away from the picturesque Candolim beach. Whether you're in the mood to indulge in a hearty pizza or relax with a cold beer while listening to live music, this venue strives to make every dining experience both delightful and unforgettable.
